data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-full bath brick ranch nestled in the heart of Huber Heights, offering a cozy and comfortable lifestyle with a host of desirable features. Located across from an elementary school and just a stone's throw away from a convenient dog park, this property is ideal for families and pet lovers alike.    With three bedrooms, this home offers room for everyone. The primary bedroom has a full bathroom for added privacy, while the two additional bedrooms share another full bathroom, making morning routines a breeze. Added family room provides additional living space just off the dining area. Windows replaced in 2009, W/D & Trane HVAC furnace and AC in 2016, Water Heater in 2023    Step outside, and you'll find a new white vinyl fenced backyard with a covered patio that provides a secure and private outdoor space. The detached 2+car garage offers ample storage and parking options, while two sheds on the property are perfect for storing your gardening tools, bikes, or outdoor equipment.    The location of this property is a standout feature. Being directly across from an elementary school means your children can enjoy a short and safe walk to school each day. For pet owners, the nearby dog park provides a fantastic opportunity for your furry friends to run and play to their hearts' content.    This Huber Heights gem combines convenience, comfort, and style, making it the perfect place to call home just minutes from the Rose Music Center, shopping, numerous restaurants, waterpark, and more.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own – schedule your viewing today and experience the best of suburban living in Ohio.    *Seller including Home Warranty by Advantage HW and will offer $2500 to be used towards closing costs or point buy down.
